"},{"b":"20.2","h":"29.11","c":"وَمَنْ","d":"nَmَw","e":"dan barang siapa"},{"b":"21.4","h":"30.41","c":"يُؤْمِنْ","d":"ۢnِmْwʾُy","e":"beriman"},{"b":"22.7","h":"32.22","c":"بِاللَّهِ","d":"ِhَّllٱِb","e":"kepada Allah"},{"b":"23.7","h":"33.82","c":"وَيَعْمَلْ","d":"ْlَmْʿعَyَw","e":"dan berbuat/beramal"},{"b":"24.6","h":"35.42","c":"صَالِحًا","d":"āًḥِlَٰṣ","e":"kebajikan/saleh"},{"b":"26.3","h":"37.54","c":"يُدْخِلْهُ","d":"ُhْlِhkْdُy","e":"Dia memasukkannya"},{"b":"27.2","h":"39.09","c":"جَنَّاتٍ","d":"ٍtَّٰnَjg","e":"surga"},{"b":"34.3","h":"41.75","c":"تَجْرِي","d":"àِrْjgَt","e":"mengalir"},{"b":"35.2","h":"43.14","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِm","e":"dari"},{"b":"36.1","h":"44.25","c":"تَحْتِهَا","d":"āَhِtْḥَt","e":"bawahnya"},{"b":"36.8","h":"45.66","c":"الْأَنْهَارُ","d":"ُrَٰhْnَaʾْlٱ","e":"sungai-sungai"},{"b":"37.9","h":"47.64","c":"خَالِدِينَ","d":"َnyِdِlَٰhk","e":"mereka kekal"},{"b":"39.1","h":"49.79","c":"فِيهَا","d":"ٓāَhyِf","e":"di dalamnya"},{"b":"41.3","h":"50.74","c":"أَبَدًا","d":"āًdَbَaʾ","e":"selama-lamanya"},{"b":"42.7","h":"55.75","c":"قَدْ","d":"ْdَq","e":"sesungguhnya"},{"b":"43.2","h":"56.15","c":"أَحْسَنَ","d":"َnَsْḥَaʾ","e":"membaguskan"},{"b":"43.9","h":"57.51","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"ُhَّllٱ","e":"Allah"},{"b":"44.6","h":"59.07","c":"لَهُ","d":"ۥُhَl","e":"kepadanya"},{"b":"45.3","h":"60.13","c":"رِزْقًا","d":"āًqْzِr","e":"rizki"}],"a":{"g":"[He sent] a Messenger [Muhammad] reciting to you the distinct verses of Allah that He may bring out those who believe and do righteous deeds from darknesses into the light. And whoever believes in Allah and does righteousness - He will admit him into gardens beneath which rivers flow to abide therein forever. Allah will have perfected for him a provision."}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.65","c":"اللَّهُ","d":"ُhَّllٱ","e":"Allah"},{"b":"0.97","h":"2.16","c":"الَّذِي","d":"àِhdَّlٱ","e":"yang"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.37","c":"خَلَقَ","d":"َqَlَhk","e":"menciptkan"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.43","c":"سَبْعَ","d":"َʿعْbَs","e":"tujuh"},{"b":"2.8","h":"5.43","c":"سَمَاوَاتٍ","d":"ٍtَٰwَٰmَs","e":"langit"},{"b":"4.7","h":"8.3","c":"وَمِنَ","d":"َnِmَw","e":"dan dari"},{"b":"5.2","h":"9.3","c":"الْأَرْضِ","d":"ِḍْrَaʾْlٱ","e":"bumi"},{"b":"6.0","h":"10.69","c":"مِثْلَهُنَّ","d":"َّnُhَlْhtِm","e":"seperti itu"},{"b":"7.7","h":"13.03","c":"يَتَنَزَّلُ","d":"ُlَّzَnَtَy","e":"turun/berlaku"},{"b":"8.8","h":"15.19","c":"الْأَمْرُ","d":"ُrْmَaʾْlٱ","e":"perintah"},{"b":"9.6","h":"16.67","c":"بَيْنَهُنَّ","d":"َّnُhَnْyَb","e":"diantara mereka/diantaranya"},{"b":"11.3","h":"27.61","c":"لِتَعْلَمُوا","d":"۟āٓwُmَlْʿعَtِl","e":"supaya kamu mengetahui"},{"b":"15.3","h":"30.67","c":"أَنَّ","d":"َّnَaʾ","e":"bahwa sesungguhnya"},{"b":"16.3","h":"32.12","c":"اللَّهَ","d":"َhَّllٱ","e":"Allah"},{"b":"17.1","h":"33.33","c":"عَلَى","d":"ٰàَlَʿع","e":"atas"},{"b":"17.7","h":"34.42","c":"كُلِّ","d":"ِّlُk","e":"segala"},{"b":"18.2","h":"35.42","c":"شَيْءٍ","d":"ٍءْàَhs","e":"sesuatu"},{"b":"19.6","h":"37.24","c":"قَدِيرٌ","d":"ٌryِdَq","e":"Maha Kuasa"},{"b":"20.9","h":"39.53","c":"وَأَنَّ","d":"َّnَaʾَw","e":"dan bahwa sesungguhnya"},{"b":"22.3","h":"41.22","c":"اللَّهَ","d":"َhَّllٱ","e":"Allah"},{"b":"23.1","h":"42.56","c":"قَدْ","d":"ْdَq","e":"sungguh/benar-benar"},{"b":"23.5","h":"43.18","c":"أَحَاطَ","d":"َṭāَḥَaʾ","e":"meliputi"},{"b":"24.4","h":"44.67","c":"بِكُلِّ","d":"ِّlُkِb","e":"dengan segala"},{"b":"25.3","h":"46.04","c":"شَيْءٍ","d":"ٍءْàَhs","e":"sesuatu"},{"b":"26.4","h":"47.54","c":"عِلْمًا","d":"āًۢmْlِʿع","e":"ilmu"}],"a":{"g":"It is Allah who has created seven heavens and of the earth, the like of them. [His] command descends among them so you may know that Allah is over all things competent and that Allah has encompassed all things in knowledge.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وعبر عن انتظار ملائكة السموات لما ينزل إليهم من القدر والأمر فقيل: ﴿ خلق سبع سموات ومن الأرض مثلهن يتنزل الأمر بينهن لتعلموا أن الله على كل شىء قدير وأن الله قد أحاط بكل شىء علما ﴾ {} وهذه أمور لا يعلم تأويلها إلا الله والراسخون في العلم وعبر ابن عباس رضى الله عنهما عن اختصاص الراسخين في العلم بعلوم لا تحتملها أفهام الخلق حيث قرأ قوله تعالى: ﴿ يتنزل الأمر بينهنّ ﴾ {} فقال لو ذكرت ما أعرفه من معنى هذه الآية لرجمتمونى وفي لفظ آخر لقلتم إنه كافر.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, He expressed the waiting of the angels of the heavens for what descends to them from the Decree [al-qadr] and the Command [al-amr], so it was said: \"He created seven heavens, and from the earth their like. The Command [al-amr] descends between them, that you may know that Allah is over all things competent and that Allah has encompassed all things in knowledge.\" And these are matters whose true interpretation [ta'wil] none knows except Allah and those firmly rooted in knowledge [al-rasikhun fi al-'ilm]. And Ibn 'Abbas, may Allah be pleased with them both, expressed the exclusive possession by those firmly rooted in knowledge [al-rasikhun fi al-'ilm] of sciences [ulum] which the understandings of creation cannot bear, when he recited the saying of the Exalted: \"The Command [al-amr] descends between them,\" and said: \"If I mentioned what I know of the meaning of this verse, you would stone me.\" And in another wording: \"You would say, 'He is an unbeliever.'\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}}}